	<div class="col-md-6">
		<h3>Automatically Assign Me Dynamic Effort Exercises</h3>
		<p>
			I will automatically enter dynamic effort exercises for you based on your weaknesses, timeframe, and available equipment.
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-6">
		<h3>Manually Select Dynamic Effort Exercises</h3>
		<p>
			I will give you a list of dynamic effort exercises for you to choose from based on your weaknesses, timeframe, and available equipment.
		</p>
	</div>
</div>
